As an example, the zinc/cerium cell has been worked on by Plurion Limited. As with the zinc/bromine cell, the negative electrode dissolves and plates zinc, Eq. 12, and at the positive electrode, cerium is shuttled between Ce(III) and Ce(IV)16\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
