For most RFB applications, the system is one phase (liquid) and so complicated expressions for multiphase flow are unnecessary, in stark contrast to low-temperature fuel cells [118]. Thus, for the convective flow one can use the Navier–Stokes equations [115]32\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
